In The Unlikely Event That Digital Files Have Been Lost, Stolen, Or Destroyed For Reasons Beyond The COMPANY’s Control, Including But Not Limited To Camera, Hard Drive, Or Equipment Malfunction, The COMPANY Liability Is Limited To The Return 50% Of The Retainer Fee Received For The EVENT(S).
